body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting our customer service department. My name is Samuel Brooks and I work with Car Dealership X. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hello, my name is Amy Gonzales.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Amy. To assist you better, could you please provide me with your phone number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, my phone number is nine eight seven six five four three two one zero.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you. Could you also provide me with your address for verification purposes?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course, my address is one two three Pine Street, City Name, State, Zip Code.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for providing that information, Amy. Is there anything else you would like to share with me today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I have concerns about the privacy of my personal information. I am feeling quite nervous about it.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I understand your concerns, Amy. Rest assured, we take customer privacy very seriously and have strict protocols in place to protect your information.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for bringing this to our attention, Amy. We appreciate your feedback and will do our best to address your concerns. Thank you for your time and have a great day!
